	<div itemprop="text"><p>I hadn&#8217;t realised there was issues with the new menu system until you mentioned it.</p>
<p>I was planning to be involved with the menu development early on, but it appeared that Scribu was leaps and bounds ahead of me in getting something up and running so I bailed out as it looked like him and others were much more suited to the development of it. Then I heard the Woo menu system was being used, which seemed odd since Scribu&#8217;s system appeared to be working fine. But it looks like there were issues with that system which aren&#8217;t going to be easy to fix <img src="http://ottopress.com/wp-content/plugins/classic-smilies/img/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>
