<p>There is always two sides to a coin. You have revealed the ugly side of the Woo menu system.  Yikes!  Thanks for popping the hood and inspecting that menu engine.  I probably won&#8217;t be taking advantage of a static menu system &#8212; egads!  For most of my menu implementations, I am using the built-in parent-child relationships for pages (not posts).</p>
